{"tid":117564,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[劇情紀錄片]Mars 火星時代","createTime":"2017-02-12T10:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T10:28:00.000Z","uid":26115,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39892046df6065341cde21764cf15b45a88149ef","tid":117564,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"《火星時代》(Mars)，是由國家地理頻道結合電影敘事手法、紀錄片影像及訪談，高規格製作的6集電視迷你劇集，模擬人類2033年登陸並拓殖火星的嘗試，以及今日科技的發展如何為17年後的太空之旅鋪路。<br />\n<br />\n2033年，首趟載人火星任務進入這座紅色星球的大氣層，但狄德勒斯號成員面臨威脅性命的緊急狀況，太空船的登陸系統斷線了。狄德勒斯號指揮官冒生命危險進行搶修，讓地球上的任務控制中心重新接收到影像。鏡頭回到現代，太空探索科技公司試圖研發全球第一具回收火箭，希望在關鍵科技取得領先，未來用來幫助人類登上火星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o8a8Ms7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo8a8Ms7.jpg&h=deb1121f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbaf272374909561fce6b11f8e711675d5726eb","tid":117564,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T09:03:55.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n睇你新果篇文就知你睇過"},{"pid":"e4d4f6c9eac54a0f7e1ffc9209b30d7e5bdc6e79","tid":117564,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:18:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e629492e677f94f8b3744f359a8daa036ab39827","tid":117564,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T01:59:31.000Z","msg":"睇左, 好睇, 高質片, 但感覺唔夠喉"},{"pid":"78733c1b5d05000b32b786c27ddfd90232543e07","tid":117564,"uid":26115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左, 好睇, 高質片, 但感覺唔夠喉</blockquote><br />\nYES，劇情同科學內容都到喉唔到肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d86de8d2264b6ceeb3a954fd2b5ea90f7fa8169","tid":117564,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:29:58.000Z","msg":"幾時出新文"},{"pid":"f0ea376864a31d1e274681cb6553a021447f4095","tid":117564,"uid":22270,"like":0,"dislike"